title: Texas to execute man who fatally shot Dallas police officer
text:
Published By: Reuters - US News - Today 
AUSTIN, Texas (Reuters) - Texas plans on Wednesday to execute Licho Escamilla, who was convicted of fatally shooting a Dallas police officer...
